All:
    esc to exit
    [ to zoom out (dim up)
    ] to zoom in (dim down)
    - fov down
    = fov up
    Arrow keys move camera
    l light on/off
    s stop/start the light movement
    . rotate light clockwise
    , rotate light counterclockwise
    9 lower light height
    0 raise light height
    m to change mode
    
